---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
---

<Layout title="Tailwind Devdude | Coder Dude">
	<main>
		<h1>
			<span class="text-gradient">Tailwind Devdude</span>
		</h1>
		<p class="instructions">
			<code class="bg-teal-700 hover:bg-sky-700 hover:text-rose-300"
				><a href="/tags/frontend">Frontend Dev Student</a></code
			> studying
			<code
				class="bg-yellow-300 text-black hover:bg-black hover:text-yellow-300"
				>JavaScript</code
			> and <code class="bg-blue-700">CSS</code>
			at <code class="bg-teal-400 text-slate-700"
				>Tailwind University</code
			>. <strong class="text-md"
				>Creating the sickest UI Library ever known to man:</strong
			>
			<code class="bg-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-500"
				><a href="#post">ChillUI</a></code
			>.
		</p>
		<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 my-10">
			<h2 class="font-bold text-gradient text-3xl mb-4">
				I make sick templates y'all!
			</h2>
			<p>
				If you've never used one of Devdude's Sick Start templates,
				you're seriously missing bro. I make my templates with the
				sickest coder chicks in mind dude and you best believe that
				they're all about lookin good and movin fast - kinda like me on
				my skis. Whooooaa whaaaaa? Chakkkeiiririrrchhhhhh! Thats me
				throwin down a ham bone knuckle wrench on a 75 degree piner dude
				- you best believe!
			</p>
		</div>
		<ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
			<Card
				href="https://docs.astro.build/"
				title="Devdude and Bulma"
				body="Yo check out my template I made with Bulma CSS, my homie!"
			/>
			<Card
				href="https://astro.build/integrations/"
				title="Devdude and Alpine.js"
				body="Yo you know I cut it up when I'm with my bestie, Alpine.js."
			/>
			<Card
				href="https://astro.build/themes/"
				title="Devdude and Next.js"
				body="It's a classic - you already know this!"
			/>
			<Card
				href="https://astro.build/chat/"
				title="Devdude and 11ty"
				body="This was like my first starter ever yo. ❤️"
			/>
		</ul>
		<div class="bg-gray-300 rounded-xl p-8 my-10">
			<h3>Yo check out my newsletter - I call it the Dudesletter!</h3>
			<p>
				Keep up to date with everything Tailwind Devdude by subscribing
				to the Dudesletter!
			</p>
			<input />
			<button
				class="bg-green-400 text-white border-solid border-black rounded-xl px-4 py-2"
				>Submit</button
			>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	:root {
		--astro-gradient: linear-gradient(0deg, #4f39fa, #da62c4);
	}

	h1 {
		margin: 2rem 0;
	}

	main {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1em;
		max-width: 60ch;
	}

	.text-gradient {
		font-weight: 900;
		background-image: var(--astro-gradient);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-size: 100% 200%;
		background-position-y: 100%;
		border-radius: 0.4rem;
		animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	@keyframes pulse {
		0%,
		100% {
			background-position-y: 0%;
		}
		50% {
			background-position-y: 80%;
		}
	}

	.instructions {
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 1rem 0;
		background: #4f39fa;
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 0.4rem;
		color: var(--color-bg);
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}

	.instructions code {
		font-size: 0.875em;
		border: 0.1em solid var(--color-border);
		border-radius: 4px;
		padding: 0.15em 0.25em;
	}

	.link-card-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(24ch, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
		padding: 0;
	}
</style>
